nation with other agents that are potentially hepatotoxic (e.', 'Moderate', 'pharmacodynamic', NULL, 'https://ddinter2.scbdd.com/server/interact/59089/', '', 'Thiotepa, Busulfan, Streptozocin, Chlorambucil, Mechlorethamine, Bendamustine, Melphalan, Ifosfamide, Melphalan flufenamide, Uracil mustard', 'Lamivudine, Paritaprevir, Glecaprevir, Tenofovir alafenamide, Maraviroc, Amprenavir, Simeprevir, Valaciclovir, Zanamivir, Cabotegravir, Lenacapavir, More', 1767369485);
